<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .order-summary { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; }
        .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; }
        .total-row { font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; color: #28a745; border-bottom: none; margin-top: 10px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 2px solid #28a745; }
        .next-steps { background: #e7f3ff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0; }
        .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .container { margin: 0 10px; } .content, .header { padding: 20px 15px; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>âœ… Order Confirmed!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for your purchase</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hi {{userName}},</h2>
        <p>Your order has been successfully processed! Here's a summary of your purchase:</p>

        <div class="order-summary">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #28a745;">ðŸ“‹ Order Summary</h3>

            <div class="detail-row">
                <span>Order Number:</span>
                <span><strong>{{orderNumber}}</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span>Event:</span>
                <span><strong>{{eventName}}</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span>Number of Tickets:</span>
                <span>{{ticketCount}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row total-row">
                <span>Total Amount:</span>
                <span>{{formatCurrency totalAmount}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>ðŸŽ¯ What's Next?</h3>
            <ol style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 15px;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Ticket Delivery:</strong> Your tickets will be sent to your email within 5 minutes</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>QR Codes:</strong> Each ticket will include a unique QR code for entry</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Event Reminder:</strong> We'll send you a reminder 24 hours before the event</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Support:</strong> Contact us if you have any questions or concerns</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 25px 0;">
            <h4>ðŸ“± Pro Tip:</h4>
            <p>Add your tickets to your mobile wallet or take screenshots of the QR codes for quick access at the venue!</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <p>Questions about your order?</p>
            <p>Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@eventhub.com" style="color: #28a745;">support@eventhub.com</a></p>
        </div>

        <p>Thank you for choosing EventHub. We hope you have an amazing time at the event!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 EventHub. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Order Number: {{orderNumber}}</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>